Interface Relation

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
RelationImpl
public interface Relation
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Relation'.

The following features are supported:

  • Domain Pattern
  • Name
  • No Checkonly Domains
  • No Enforced Domains
  • No When
  • No Where
  • No Domains
  • No Vars
  • Val Out
  • Fan Out
  • Fan In
  • No Bound Vars
  • No Unbound Vars
  • Var Binding Rate
  • Avg Size Of Domain Pattern
  • Is Leaf
  • Depth Of Leaf
  • Nwwp
  • Nwwpc

See Also:
QVTMetricsPackage.getRelation()
